                        <interp inst="t17720603-44-victim453" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , did make an assault putting him in corporal fear and danger of his life, and stealing from his person sixty leather bags, value 20 s. the property of our Sovereign Lord 
                     <persName id="t17720603-44-victim454" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t17720603-44-viclabel206" type="occupation">the King</rs>
                        <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17720603-44-victim454 t17720603-44-viclabel206"></join>
