               <p>Q. Do you know who wrote the writing on it?</p>
               <p>Brown. Yes, I wrote it; Guyant gave it to my husband.</p>
               <p>John Brown. I gave a 20 l. note to my wife.</p>
               <p>Q. Is that your wife's writing?</p>
               <p>Brown. I believe it is; I had it from Guyant.</p>
